#### Step 2: Update Your Contact Form HTML

Now, we just need to add one small piece of information to your contact form to tell it where to go after submission.

1.  Open your `src/contact.njk` file.
2.  Find the opening `<form>` tag. It currently looks like this:
    ```html
    <form name="contact" method="POST" netlify>
    ```
3.  Add an `action` attribute to it that points to your new "Thank You" page, like this:
    ```html
    <form name="contact" method="POST" action="/thank-you/" netlify>
    ```
